Keep @Double Berry Cobbler{2%unit} frozen or refrigerated until ready to eat; best if used within 7 days.

If frozen, thaw in the #refrigerator{} (at 40 degrees) overnight or for ~{2-3%hours} at room temperature before eating.

Enjoy cold, at room temperature, or heat in the #microwave{}.

**MICROWAVE:** Remove and discard plastic wrapping. Microwave thawed product until warmed through, ~{30-45%seconds}. Do not overheat.

> Psst—we highly recommend serving with a scoop of vanilla ice cream on top.